zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sgr1665702797426.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sgr1665702797426.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sgr1665702797426.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sgr1665702797426\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Glyph Library \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to load a new glyph or view the properties and image of existing glyphs.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__p_d6743e1_d6744e1_d6745e1\">You can use a glyph as an icon, a background for a component, or as image data in the application.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__section_brs_hwf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d786523e58\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__ul_hgz_3wf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3314e1_d3315e1_d3316e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Glyph</span>\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3317e1_d3318e1_d3319e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cfv1665702708639.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cfv1665702708639.html\" title=\"Language code for the global object with which you are working.\">Language</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3320e1_d3321e1_d3322e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__p_d6749e1_d6750e1_d6751e1\">The following properties are derived from the original image\n        and cannot be changed.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__ul_kgz_3wf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3323e1_d3324e1_d3325e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Height</span>—height of the glyph in\n          pixels; read-only. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3326e1_d3327e1_d3328e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Width</span>—width of the glyph in\n          pixels; read-only.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3329e1_d3330e1_d3331e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Colors</span>—number of colors used in\n          the image; read-only </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__p_d6752e1_d6753e1_d6754e1\">Glyphs are only supported for Windows platforms, so the\n        properties <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">GUI</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">GUI-Specific</span>, and\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Full-Color</span> cannot be modified:</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__section_ccs_kwf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d786523e130\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__ul_j3h_lwf_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3332e1_d3333e1_d3334e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cpe1705582470714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cpe1705582470714.html\" title=\"Glyphs are maintained and deployed in a runtime library.\">Create and Maintain Glyphs</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3335e1_d3336e1_d3337e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vng1705582774408.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vng1705582774408.html\" title=\"You cannot modify a glyph directly in Uniface. You must first export the image to a file and modify it using your preferred image editor, before replacing the glyph in Uniface.\">Modifying Glyphs</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__li_d3338e1_d3339e1_d3340e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnd1705582899319.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnd1705582899319.html\" title=\"You can use glyphs in form components and widgets, panels, menus, and drag-and-drop formats.\">Using Glyphs</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__section_pr4_lwf_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d786523e166\">Menu Options</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Menu Options for Glyph Editor</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">Menu Option </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">Action </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Open/New</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">Open or create a new library. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Close</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">Close the editor. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Save</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">Save the glyph. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Delete Library</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">Delete the current glyph library. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; New Glyph</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Create a new global object</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; Duplicate <var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Global Object Type&gt;</var>\n</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Save a copy of the current global object under a different name.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; Delete Glyph</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Delete the current glyph.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; Compile Glyph</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compile the current glyph.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; Unload</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Export the glyph as a <span class=\"ph filepath\">.bmp</span> image file.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View &gt;Zoom Field</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Edit the selected field in a separate dialog; useful when editing text blocks and\n                  code.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View &gt;Message Frame</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Display the message frame; useful after compiling the object.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Go To <var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Global Object Type&gt;</var>\n</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sgr1665702797426__table_d581e1_d582e1_d583e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Create or open a different type of global object library.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ush1665702873697.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Glyphs</a><p>Glyphs are images in a Uniface-proprietary format, which can be used as background images in forms, entities and application shells, and as icons in widgets, panel buttons, menus, and drag-and-drop formats.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531966\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Glyph Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Glyph Library Use this editor to load a new glyph or view the properties and image of existing glyphs. You can use a glyph as an icon, a background for a component, or as image data in the application. Properties Glyph Name Language Description The following properties are derived from the original image and cannot be changed. Height —height of the glyph in pixels; read-only. Width —width of the glyph in pixels; read-only. Colors —number of colors used in the image; read-only Glyphs are only supported for Windows platforms, so the properties GUI , GUI-Specific , and Full-Color cannot be modified: How to Create and Maintain Glyphs Modifying Glyphs Using Glyphs Menu Options Table 1. Menu Options for Glyph Editor Menu Option Action File > Open/New Open or create a new library. File > Close Close the editor. File > Save Save the glyph. File > Delete Library Delete the current glyph library. Edit > New Glyph Create a new global object Edit > Duplicate <Global Object Type> Save a copy of the current global object under a different name. Edit > Delete Glyph Delete the current glyph. Edit > Compile Glyph Compile the current glyph. Edit > Unload Export the glyph as a .bmp image file. View >Zoom Field Edit the selected field in a separate dialog; useful when editing text blocks and code. View >Message Frame Display the message frame; useful after compiling the object. Go To <Global Object Type> Create or open a different type of global object library. Related Links Glyphs Glyphs are images in a Uniface-proprietary format, which can be used as background images in forms, entities and application shells, and as icons in widgets, panel buttons, menus, and drag-and-drop formats. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}